<p>Hi,</p>
<p>I work for a TEFL provider,Online TEFL Courses, and I think it might be quite difficult to get a teaching job without a degree.</p>
<p>In terms of the qualification you do, I would go for a 120-hour as this is the most sought after by employers.  Our courses are good quality and are the most accredited in the UK.</p>
<p>Thanks,</p>
<p>Richard</p>
