<p>I saw your post on the Saigonist and I was wonder=<br />
if you have any information about getting a job without a degree. I am a s=<br />
tudent at UNLV in Nevada, United States and I have my TEFL, but I also don'=<br />
t have my BA yet. I've read in many places that to get a work permit you ne=<br />
ed a BA. I am wondering if you've had any luck finding any jobs without you=<br />
r BA? Also, what do you think the risks are of working without a permit? Ma=<br />
ybe deportation? Anyway, let's chat and share info. I can be reached at 702=<br />
349 7799 or <a href="../../cdn-cgi/l/email-protection.html" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="3956545c504c4a58515c4b56794058515656175a5654">[email&#160;protected]</a></p>
