<p>$3000 AUD is plenty of money to survive for a few months. It will not take you that long to find some teaching work. When you arrive you should chat with other expats that have been here for awhile and are teaching English. They will give you tips, but better yet they can give you contacts at schools. There are plenty of English teachers hanging out in the alleys of the backpacker district (alleys of Pham Ngu Lao).</p>
